## 🎯 Core Principles

### 1. TDD — NON-NEGOTIABLE
`RED → GREEN → REFACTOR`. Never write code before a failing test. Keep coverage ≥80%. All tests pass before commit.
→ See [.docs/TDD.md](./.docs/TDD.md)

### 2. Layered Architecture — STRICT
`Component → Composable → Store ⇄ Repository → API`. Never skip layers; each layer has one responsibility.
→ See [.docs/ARCHITECTURE.md](./.docs/ARCHITECTURE.md)

### 3. Permission-Based Access — 2-LEVEL
Page level via `definePageMeta({ middleware: 'permission', permissions: ['resource.action'] })`
and component level via `v-if="hasPermission('resource.action')"`.
→ See [.docs/PERMISSIONS.md](./.docs/PERMISSIONS.md)

