## 📋 Essential Rules

- **ESLint / TypeScript — zero tolerance**: no `any`, no unused vars, strict mode. Run `npm run lint` before commit.
- **i18n everything**: never hardcode user-facing text — always `t('key')`. → [.docs/I18N.md](./.docs/I18N.md)
- **Error handling**: never `useToast()` directly — always `useToaster()`. Handle loading/empty/error states.
  → [.docs/ERROR-HANDLING.md](./.docs/ERROR-HANDLING.md)
- **Forms**: PrimeVue + Zod + vee-validate. → [.docs/FORMS.md](./.docs/FORMS.md)
- **Tables & filters**: no currency symbols in filter inputs; currency uses min-max range; MultiSelect values
  are plain arrays. → [.docs/TABLES.md](./.docs/TABLES.md)

