## ✅ Pre-Commit Checklist

- [ ] Tests written first (TDD), all pass, coverage ≥80%
- [ ] `npm run type-check` — no errors; ESLint + Stylelint pass
- [ ] Page + component permissions set
- [ ] Error / loading / empty states handled
- [ ] i18n keys added (no hardcoded text)
